ABL Asset Management Company Limited
fields.description:
ABL Asset Management Company Limited is a subsidiary of Allied Bank Limited, one of the largest banks in Pakistan. ABL Asset Management Company Limited offers a range of mutual funds to individual and institutional investors in Pakistan. These include equity funds, income funds, and balanced funds, among others.

The company's mutual funds are managed by a team of experienced investment professionals who use a disciplined, research-driven approach to identify investment opportunities and manage risk. ABL Asset Management Company Limited is regulated by the Securities and Exchange Commission of Pakistan (SECP) and is committed to meeting the highest standards of corporate governance and compliance.

fields.name: AKD Investment Management Limited
fields.description:
AKD Investment Management Limited is a leading asset management company based in Pakistan that offers a range of mutual funds and other investment products to individual and institutional investors. The company is a subsidiary of AKD Group, a well-respected financial services group in Pakistan.

AKD Investment Management Limited's mutual funds are managed by a team of experienced investment professionals who use a disciplined, research-driven approach to identify investment opportunities and manage risk. The company is regulated by the Securities and Exchange Commission of Pakistan (SECP) and is committed to meeting the highest standards of corporate governance and compliance.

In addition to its mutual funds, AKD Investment Management Limited also offers a range of other investment products, including pension funds, real estate investment trusts (REITs), and structured finance solutions. The company has a strong track record of performance and is known for its commitment to delivering value to its clients.
